Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:05.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A large contingent of Roman forces has appeared on the border between Seize and Nomansland?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:26.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A'ishah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:30.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that gunshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:37.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have captured the Roman soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:38.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:40.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No. She is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:41.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:47.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our battalion will now join forces with the First and Third Divisions in transit to the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:48.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:49.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:51.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you move, I will shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:53.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:56.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:01:00.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Command your troops to leave the fortress immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:03.20,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}Echo Through the Blue Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:06.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:07.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Treason!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.66,0:01:11.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those girls in the fortress have taken our commanding officer hostage and barricaded themselves in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:12.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:18.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, it didn't hit any of her major organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:19.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.52,0:01:21.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her condition should stay stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:23.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sister Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:27.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:31.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl was going to be a sacrifice to start the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:33.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't be worth much dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.47,0:01:34.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:38.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This last month,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:43.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,we've been following Roman forces as they mobilized for an attack from a rear front.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:48.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably another bargaining chip in the peace conferences.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:51.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They took us lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:55.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Archduke has cold feet - he specifically ordered us not to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.87,0:02:00.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So we need one little push so they attack us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:06.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A little push, like a prisoner of war,\N executed by firing squad, crying and screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:08.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace is just a worthless play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:12.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rome must be thrown into ruin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:15.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so, Noël Kannagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:19.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, our hero, the Witch of Helvetia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:22.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I wouldn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:26.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Noël was just used by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:28.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Noël...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:32.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really were involved with the Invisible Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:34.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Invisible Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:40.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest genius the Academy has known in over a hundred years - the Invisible Death -
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:44.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who restored that ancient biological weapons plant
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:45.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,is the girl sitting before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:50.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your talent is wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:51.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to work under me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:03.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock this man in the distillery downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:09.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our compatriots are already in transit for battle with the Roman army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:12.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One small tap and the scenario will play itself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's back to the battlefield for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:21.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when you think it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got some bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:27.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colonel has been locked in the distillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:29.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:40.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and eat these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sweets I stocked up on in Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:44.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naomi, you're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:49.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave when it really gets bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:55.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all completely messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:58.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of the Fire protect the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:01.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're throwing the town into the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:04.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were hiding,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:09.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the legend of the Maidens of the Fire from Miss A'ishah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:17.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that a completely different legend was passed down in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:22.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of the Fire protect life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:47.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the shift change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:50.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't need to. I can't leave you to do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:54.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can shoot a gun at someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:01.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If I think that it's the right thing to do, I might.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:06.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the Maidens of the Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:09.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the Maidens of the Fire before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:15.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What, do you actually believe that story? That fairy tale that Roman made up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Something about it clicks with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of the Fire protect life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:27.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it must have been that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:30.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:55.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how good her ears are,\N she can't possibly hear it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A cease-fire signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:59.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:03.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:05.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:15.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She might have just heard things. And even if it were, we don't know if the treaty has been signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:18.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, we must inform Colonel Hopkins that-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:23.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency! When I went to bring him food, the Colonel wasn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:30.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence attack in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:31.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the Colonel will actually listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:42.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in not trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:47.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:52.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colonel laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:58.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When he saw the people dead from the Death I resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:00.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:05.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He will kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:08.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Until there's no one left to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:13.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I helped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:19.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think so, then save more lives than you took.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A'ishah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Cease-fire? Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can trust her ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:35.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We'll vouch for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:40.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's easily amused, she forgets everything, she's just like a little kid, and she's not sexy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest this old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want war that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:50.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,War advances civilization and science.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:53.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to restore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Man's former glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:58.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:02.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Roman army is set to attack tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:07.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's no way to stop the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:10.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naomi was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:28.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy! We're up against the Demon of Binnenland!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to deliver it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone gave me this sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:37.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You are being selfish. You do not do things because you decide them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:45.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone once said that the world was already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:49.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I love this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:53.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this town. I love everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:58.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:06.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:09.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A'ishah is begging you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:34.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:39.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You... Same...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You have suffered enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:58.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:17.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, A'ishah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:30.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go, there's no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:33.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,have no objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:50.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:52.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:58.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been objecting for us this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:03.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:07.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,want someone my age...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:12.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,going through torture either! But Rio isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:18.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And Noël and Kanata are lax...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:23.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So I had to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:27.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm such a bad commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:36.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:36.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:40.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,O, myriad gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,may your blessings be upon the Maidens of the Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Primary converter reactor output rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:59.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,FAP, FAC, DMR, and ECP all green.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:03.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Superconducting circuits, function stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:05.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire control system also good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:09.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Primary and secondary armaments are operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:11.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Release all joint locks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:18.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Weight-reduction system operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:21.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Factor of minus... about five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepared to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:28.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We do it just like we practiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, my little ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:31.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:32.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Main armament, standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:34.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Load shell! AP round!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Loading AP round!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:46.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Target locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:49.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:06.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:11.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:49.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:50.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They're in that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:50.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemicaduchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:54.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To restore the pinnacle of ancient technology...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:59.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal all units! All possible measures to prevent escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:02.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We've had enough of your war!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:06.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:09.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to get them, get us first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:10.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:11.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Demon of Binnenland.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:31.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Go around! Join with the forces at our rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of the Fire protect life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:45.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is in your hands, Miss Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:52.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:55.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,long before the world turned out this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:15:01.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,An angel that God sent to deliver divine retribution upon the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:06.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,was injured, and set her wings down to rest in a town at the Western end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:17.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the maidens that lived in the fortress that saved her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:22.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the one sent to bring them ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:27.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the maidens took pity upon the angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:30.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,With the aid of a giant spider,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:33.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,they sheltered the angel in the valley below.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:39.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To stifle the blood springing from her, the maidens,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:42.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,each in turn, held the head of the angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:49.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And in thanks, the angel granted them a golden horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:56.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But eventually, the people of the town learned of the angel's presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}and set fire to the bottom of the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:03.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The maidens were lost to the fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:05.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the angel's head taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:08.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and their suffering ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:17.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, the host of angels appeared, filling the sky above the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:21.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, a miracle happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:24.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the sky echoed on high,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:27.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and the angels departed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:37.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,With her last breath, the last maiden of the fortress sounded the golden horn
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:40.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and saved the lives of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:56.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you remember that young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:58.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The one you gave the caramel to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:02.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to get thrown into this too, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:04.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All units, prepare to charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:08.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't do anything about that. We're soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:24.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:28.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:34.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an allied vehicle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Under command of...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Platoon 1121!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A cease-fire signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:03.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's a Roman signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:06.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major General!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:09.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't pull back now! Main armament, standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No. They're not stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:14.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:05.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That young lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:10.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:12.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:13.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! You will fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:15.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Both sides, lay down your arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:33.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am second in line to the throne of Helvetia,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:38.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,daughter of the royal family of Helvetia,\N fiancée of the Emperor of the Holy Roman Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:41.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio Kazumiya Arkadia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am here in the name of my father, the Archduke of Helvetia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:48.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and the name of the Roman Emperor, to announce:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:52.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have peace! There will be no more fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:55.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Both sides will disband immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:58.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an imperial command!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:05.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who do not comply will be punished by the First Royal Guard of Helvetia under both names!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:06.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:16.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to fight anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:48.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:51.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:54.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.10,0:22:26.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure feels like spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:31.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, Noël, what did A'ishah say in her letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.31,0:22:37.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Translate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:41.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am well. I am practicing the trumpet every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:43.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.01,0:22:47.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We even get letters from Rome,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:50.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but we still don't get any from the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:52.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's just really busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:55.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio is a princess, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.07,0:23:00.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I mean, she was surrounded by the Royal Guard back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.91,0:23:03.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't even talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.05,0:23:05.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Klaus's bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:15.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.03,0:23:17.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, new recruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.43,0:23:18.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to beat-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:42.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, I have been assigned to Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:45.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Lieutenant Rio Kazumiya Arkadia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:49.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Filicia Heidemann, requesting permission to perform duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.45,0:23:51.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Permission granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.30,0:23:54.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no ranks here, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:24:02.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Well, the Roman Emperor is actually a pretty reasonable guy and, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.43,0:24:07.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,he told me he would grant me one wish as thanks for ending the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.71,0:24:09.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.55,0:24:14.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.99,0:24:16.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:18.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.73,0:24:21.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Welcome home, Rio.
